content:
Add the Site Banner Component to Your Sites

To let users add a banner to your Aura and LWR sites, add the Site Banner component to your site in Experience Builder. You can also customize the look and feel of your banner.

Available in: Lightning Experience with your standard Service Cloud license
From Setup, enter Customer Service Incident Management, and then click Customer Service Incident Management.
Under Set Up Broadcast Site Banner, find Add Banner to Sites, and select Go to Digital Experiences.
Find the sites that you assigned broadcast topics to and select Builder.
From the Components panel, select Site Banner, and add it to your site layout.
Optionally, configure the site banner height, font, and colors.
Publish your changes.

Give your users access.
